{"id": "1517589862662930432", "channel_id": "1517589862662930432", "type": 0, "author_id": "1157913973807661076", "author_name": "purple_orange233", "author_bot": false, "content": "融灾界面能不能压缩一下，信息量本来就不多，凹完炫耀时截屏还得截2次。\n\n或者加一点信息量？把命轮和钥令也放在外面不用点进去看。", "timestamp": "2026-06-19T18:00:18.715000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "✅", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1517589862662930432", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "融灾界面改一下", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"], "is_thread_starter": true}
{"id": "1517589506143031556", "channel_id": "1517589506143031556", "type": 0, "author_id": "1437487264023318668", "author_name": "vxvendetta97", "author_bot": false, "content": "For special deals, like the Dreamy Rendezvous pack, that you need to complete a set of missions to get all the rewards, like clearing chapter 4 of the story. Is a problem that it will go away even if you pay for it, locking you out of some of them.\n\nThis discourage potential buyers that joined late, because they may not have the time to complete the missions. Losing a potential investor in the game. \n\nI would recommend that, if a person buy a pack with missions, it is at least extended for 2 weeks, to help them to unlock the rewards, if not just make it permanent for them until all rewards are cleared.\n\nWould that be possible?", "timestamp": "2026-06-19T17:58:53.714000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-06-19T18:00:38.116000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "Celeste_agree", "emoji_id": "1400771815076528258", "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1517589506327445564", "filename": "saya_04.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 40406, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1517589506143031556/1517589506327445564/saya_04.png?ex=6a38cf1d&is=6a377d9d&hm=ebe64080a2054a284cd749292db05e39ea6ffe1c8d8be2f5ed8da3244500a712&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1517589506143031556", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Paid packs and timed missions", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497", "1361168939622727801"], "is_thread_starter": true}
