{"id": "1517624028632846397", "channel_id": "1497031596434260119", "type": 19, "author_id": "422766128826417152", "author_name": "blackdonut5182", "author_bot": false, "content": "I believe it is up to the user's choice whether to enjoy the game slowly or quickly.\n\nTo understand the story in order, it is best to progress through the main story and sub-stories simultaneously, but the current system makes this difficult.\n\nIt would have been fine if the sub-stories were simple event-based narratives unrelated to the main story, but since that is not the case,\n\nI consider the current side stories to be an extension of the main story.", "timestamp": "2026-06-19T20:16:04.517000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-06-19T20:18:39.867000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": ["231543819026300928"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1497279445378011287", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1497031596434260119", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Reality Verges", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801"]}
